Title: 5 coolest things you'll find at GitHub Universe 2025
Description:
Get a sneak peek behind the scenes at GitHub Universe 2025! We found 5 insanely cool things you won't want to miss, from a hacked Furby army and an Iron Man-style glove to playable conference badges and a build-your-own Copilot station. See what makes Universe the can't-miss developer event of the year.
